data.description: Welcome home to this charming 2 bedroom raised ranch that's just minutes away from Downtown Monroe! Step inside and you'll find a well maintained interior that features a desirable open floor plan, spacious bedrooms, convenient first floor laundry and more. The beautiful eat-in kitchen is the true heart of this home! Boasting ample counter space, modern appliances, and room for dining. The extra large backyard is perfect for entertaining and the full basement offers great additional storage space. Brand new sewer line, newer roof, hot water tank and updated electrical. Schedule your tour today!
